Class Project

java.lang.Object
Project
public class Project extends Object
Represents a public housing project managed by HDB. Contains attributes related to housing types, availability, pricing, and application management.

    • Project

      public Project(String title, String neighbourhood, int numof2room, int price2room, int numof3room, int price3room, LocalDate opening_date, LocalDate closing_date, HDBManager managerIC, int numOfOfficerSlots)
      Constructs a new Project with the specified attributes.
      Parameters:
      title - Title of the project.
      neighbourhood - Neighbourhood where the project is located.
      numof2room - Number of 2-room flats available.
      price2room - Price of a 2-room flat.
      numof3room - Number of 3-room flats available.
      price3room - Price of a 3-room flat.
      opening_date - Opening date for applications.
      closing_date - Closing date for applications.
      managerIC - HDBManager in charge of the project.
      numOfOfficerSlots - Number of officers allowed to manage the project.
